    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. The exterior finish is flawless, boasting a deep, factory-fresh luster without a single scratch, swirl mark, or stone chip. Inside, the cabin is pristine; the upholstery shows no signs of wear, the dashboard is perfect, and all original features and electronics operate exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in peak condition, having been meticulously maintained with a smooth, powerful engine and a transmission that shifts seamlessly. This is a rare find for a buyer seeking a vehicle that has been preserved in a climate-controlled environment and treated with the utmost care.",
      "price": 49000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle in truly showroom-pristine condition. Meticulously maintained and kept in a climate-controlled environment, this specimen represents the pinnacle of its class. From the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior upholstery, every detail reflects a standard of care that is increasingly difficult to find. Mechanically sound and visually stunning, this vehicle offers an unparalleled driving experience for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! It truly breaks my heart to even think about parting with this beauty, but it\u2019s time for her to find a new home where she\u2019ll be just as pampered. I\u2019ve spent countless weekends making sure every inch shines like the day she rolled off the lot\u2014honestly, she\u2019s in such incredible shape you\u2019d think she was kept in a time capsule! From the spotless, fresh-smelling interior to that smooth-as-silk engine, she\u2019s a total dream to drive. You might find a tiny, microscopic speck if you really hunt for it, but to any normal eye, she's absolute perfection. Come on over, let\u2019s grab a coffee, and I\u2019ll show you why this is the one you\u2019ve been waiting for!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a concours-level E46 M3 that redefines the 'mint' designation. This S54 powerplant exhibits surgical precision, with the double-VANOS system recently overhauled to ensure optimal cam phasing and instantaneous low-end torque delivery. The subframe has been proactively reinforced with precision-welded plates, neutralizing the chassis's inherent structural vulnerabilities. We\u2019ve dialed in the suspension geometry for maximum turn-in bite, utilizing high-durometer bushings that eliminate lateral compliance for unparalleled feedback through the steering rack. Every fluid service has been performed at half-intervals using high-zinc synthetics to preserve rod bearing tolerances and valvetrain integrity. This isn't just a driver\u2019s car; it\u2019s a mechanical masterpiece with negligible parasitic loss and a throttle response that borders on telepathic. If you demand a chassis that remains perfectly flat through the apex and an inline-six that sings to 8,000 RPM without a hint of hesitation, this is the specimen for your collection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Flawless. Showroom condition. Zero defects. Mechanically perfect. First to see will buy. Act fast.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine a machine that doesn't just travel through space, but through time. This isn't merely a vehicle; it\u2019s a preserved moment of automotive perfection, a rolling sculpture that demands the sunset as its backdrop. Every curve of its glass-like finish reflects a life of pampered luxury, and the interior\u2014a sanctuary of hand-stitched leather\u2014still carries the faint, intoxicating scent of a brand-new legacy. To drive it is to command a symphony of precision engineering that feels as vital and spirited today as the moment it first left the factory. This is more than a purchase; it is the acquisition of a masterpiece, a rare chance to own a pristine relic of a golden era.",
      "price": 48500.0,
